OL,3,CWigan Warriors legend Billy Boston
OL,4,Cknighted at Buckingham Palace
OL,6,FFor the first time in rugby league's
OL,7,F130 year history one of its greatest
OL,8,Fplayers has been knighted.
OL,10,FWigan Warriors legend Sir Billy Boston
OL,11,Fhas become the first person from his
OL,12,Fsport to be presented with a
OL,13,Fknighthood at a ceremony at Buckingham
OL,14,FPalace on Tuesday, June 10.
OL,16,FSpeaking after the ceremony, he told
OL,17,FITV News "I've enjoyed myself".
