OL,3,CWigan Warriors legend Billy Boston
OL,4,Cknighted at Buckingham Palace
OL,6,FHis son Stephen told ITV News that it
OL,7,F"was a really great honour. I think it
OL,8,Fhas come a little bit late, it
OL,9,Fshould've been a little bit earlier,
OL,10,Fso he could enjoy it a little bit more
OL,11,Fbecause obviously his dementia, but
OL,12,Fwe're really, really pleased and
OL,13,Fhonoured to be given this honour for
OL,14,Fmy dad."
OL,16,FSir Billy said it was "a real honour"
OL,17,Fto meet the King.
OL,19,FSir Billy Boston and his son Stephen
OL,20,Fspeaking to ITV's Chris Hall:
