OL,6,FSir Billy's son Stephen said this
OL,7,Fhonour had "really capped off his
OL,8,F(father's) career in full.
OL,10,F"It was an honour that was due a long,
OL,11,Flong time ago, and its the first rugby
OL,12,Fleague player ever and I think that
OL,13,Fshould change. There should be some
OL,14,Fmore rugby league players brought into
OL,15,Fthe knighthood."
