OL,4,Cknighted at Buckingham Palace
OL,6,FWigan Warriors owner Mike Danson told
OL,7,Fthe club's website: "One of the
OL,8,Fbiggest thrills in my ownership of
OL,9,FWigan Rugby League Club has been
OL,10,Fenjoying the company of Billy Boston.
OL,11,FWithout doubt Billy was a player who
OL,12,Fwas ` and still is ` the biggest crowd
OL,13,Ffavourite in Rugby League.
OL,15,F"He is my mum Jean's favourite player
OL,16,F` they are of the same age! She
OL,17,Fremains in awe of the great man and
OL,18,Fhis Rugby League legacy.
