OL,6,F"I am therefore thrilled that at long
OL,7,Flast, Billy will be appointed as Rugby
OL,8,FLeague's first Knight! A richly
OL,9,Fdeserved honour which means this most
OL,10,Fhumble of men, rightly receives at
OL,11,Flast, fitting recognition for his
OL,12,Fextraordinary efforts. Many
OL,13,Fcongratulations to Billy, his wife
OL,14,FJoan and the family on this
OL,15,Fmagnificent achievement."
